name: COVID19SNOMEDValueSetForSeizureDisorders
title: COVID19 SNOMED Value Set for Seizure Disorders
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to recurrent seizures or epilepsy and is listed as a neurologic disorder on the CDC SARS-CoV-2 hospitalization surveillance case report form.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes recurrent or intractable seizures and epilepsy.),(Exclusion Criteria: )
